      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The tool processes the spectral library by iteratively executing all steps for each entry until no new metadata is found... Since it takes some non-trivial time for the services to respond to a query, this task is suitable for the asynchronous approach, making the tool computationally efficient.",
