      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "The paper describes MSMetaEnhancer's current functionality (querying external services, logging issues) but does not describe or propose a Monitor class, health metrics aggregation system, or JSON report generation. This appears to be a proposed feature extension rather than something documented in the paper.",
