      "asbval:note": "Paper demonstrates RDKit-based local computation for identifier conversion (molecular weight from SMILES), but does not explicitly describe SMILES\u2194InChI round-trip validation or bidirectional conversion testing. The paper supports the concept of local RDKit-based ComputeConverter but the specific validation methodology (round-trip testing, structural equivalence checking) is not mentioned.",
