      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Validate the chemical correctness and consistency of local SMILES\u2194InChI conversions by performing bidirectional conversions on test molecules and comparing structural equivalence. This ensures that a ComputeConverter subclass using RDKit produces chemically valid and reversible t",
