    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/spectral-metadata-enrichment/008",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "import asyncio from MSMeta Enhancer import Application app = Application()... asyncio.run(app.annotate_spectra(services, jobs))... Any issues regarding the annotation process (such as the absence of target data or unavailability of a service) are recorded in a detailed log file, which can be specified as an optional output of the tool.",
      "asbval:note": "Application class and asynchronous annotation pipeline confirmed. Log file for recording issues confirmed. However, no explicit mention of 'Logger' class or 'coverage metrics' functionality in the passages\u2014these may be implementation details not documented in the paper.",
